<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Capital" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Capital,</orth> adj. 1) chief, principal: <cit><quote>military title c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.2.110" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 2, 110</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>she is our c. demand,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 5.2.96" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V, 2, 96</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>so c. a calf,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.111" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 2, 111</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) punishable by loss of life: <cit><quote>in such c. kind,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 3.3.81" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. III, 3, 81</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>so c. in nature,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 4.7.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 7, 7</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>c. crimes,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 2.2.56" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 2, 56</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>offences,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.823" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 823</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. per 2.4.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. II, 4, 5</bibl>. <cit><quote>treason,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 4.151" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 IV, 151</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.2.109" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B IV, 2, 109</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 5.1.107" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B V, 1, 107</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 1.3.115" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 3, 115</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 5.3.83" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. V, 3, 83</bibl>.
<lb />3) mortal, pernicious: <cit><quote>to poor we thine enmity 's most c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 5.3.104" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. V, 3, 104</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>